\pard\tx1080\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi-910\sb80\sa0\li1080\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Bar 6:	the two whole-note g's can be in voice 1.\par
