\pard\tx1080\tx2880\tx4320\tx5760\qj\fi-910\sb80\sa0\li1080\ri0\f0\fs24\b0\i0\ul0\strike0\scaps0\cf0 Bar 12:	the down-stemmed notes in the treble staff can be in voice 1.   The up-stemmed notes in the bass staff can be set in voice 2, which drops out early.\par
